        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Rank Math is a top AI SEO plugin for WordPress, offering a highly comprehensive free tier, advanced schema markup, Content AI scoring, keyword rank tracking from your dashboard, and seamless integration with Google Search Console and Analytics."
      }
