    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Which AI SEO tool is best for agencies?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Semrush is a top AI SEO tool for agencies due to its comprehensive feature set, white-label reporting, client management tools, competitor analysis, and scalable pricing. For smaller agencies, Frase combined with Surfer SEO offers a cost-effective alternative."
