<h3>Test Results</h3>
<p><strong>Test scenario:</strong> Keyword research for "AI content marketing tools" — analyzed top 50 competing domains</p>
<ul>
<li>Keywords discovered: 4,230+ in under 30 seconds</li>
<li>Keyword difficulty accuracy: 9.2/10 — closely matched real SERP competition</li>
<li>Content score correlation: 8.8/10 — SEO Writing Assistant aligned well with ranking pages</li>
<li>Site audit issues detected: 47 (with prioritized fixes)</li>
